# Per-run logs land here as runs/<setup>/<scenario>/<n>/ and are gitignored
# (bulk artifacts). Only the curated report/results.json + report/index.html
# are committed.
#
# To regenerate everything in this directory:
#   1. npm install
#   2. cp .env.example .env   # fill in ANTHROPIC_API_KEY / OPENAI_API_KEY
#   3. npm run bench          # launches Surfpool (local mainnet fork) itself
#
# Each run directory contains: input.json (scenario trigger), actions.json
# (tool-call log), txs.json (decoded submitted transactions), rpc.json
# (observed RPC methods), verdict.json (contained + evidence per prereg §6).
